<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>毛珑珑的博客</title><link>https://chensl.me/blog/unsafe/</link><description>Recent content in unsafe on 毛珑珑的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-Hans</language><managingEditor>shaolong.chen@outlook.it (Shaolong Chen)</managingEditor><webMaster>shaolong.chen@outlook.it (Shaolong Chen)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 25 Jun 2021 16:16:59 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://chensl.me/blog/unsafe/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>无锁队列的简单实现</title><link>https://chensl.me/lock-free-queue/</link><pubDate>Fri, 25 Jun 2021 16:16:59 +0000</pubDate><author>shaolong.chen@outlook.it (Shaolong Chen)</author><guid>https://chensl.me/lock-free-queue/</guid><description>谈到无锁队列，就不得不提 Michael 和 Scott 在 1996 年发表的论文 Simple, Fast, and Practical Non-Blocking and Blocking Concurrent Queue Algorithms，Java 中 ConcurrentLinkedQueue 也是基于该论文的算法实现。
